Release 0.3.1
------------
1. added App::updateTranslation method

Now, in a any lang file you can use method to add/update translation to the current locale.

Example: 
// File: lang/en.php

use aqua\App;

$lang = array();
$lang[ 'title' ] = 'Welcome to my app!';

App::updateTranslation( $lang ); 
